description.original: Reminder plugin for Obsidian. This plugin adds feature to manage TODOs with reminder.
description.translation: Obsidian 提醒插件。此插件添加了使用提醒管理 TODO 的功能。

dict..desc(\"Time when a reminder with no tim: .desc("当没有设置具体时间时的提醒时间"
dict..desc(\"Use system notification for remi: .desc("使用系统通知进行提醒通知"
dict..desc(\"Line-separated list of remind me: .desc("行分隔的提醒我以后的项目列表"
dict..desc(\"When toggled, Dates link to dail: .desc("切换时，日期链接到每日笔记。"
